Orders

Expect 1-3 days of processing time before orders ship

  • Standard Shipping: 4-7 day delivery after orders ship - $7(Free on orders over $75)
  • Expedited Shipping: 2-4 day delivery after orders ship - $15
  • Express Shipping: 1-2 day delivery after orders ship - $20

SHIPPING & DELIVERY

Reebok UNLOCKED members receive free standard shipping, returns and exchanges on all orders. Already a member? LOG IN. Not a member? JOIN NOW.

  • P.O. Box and Military APO/FPO items will be shipped via USPS within 3-8 full business days. Business days are Monday - Friday, excluding federal holidays within the United States.

Gift Cards

  • USPS First Class 2-8 business days - $1.95
  • FedEx 2 Day, 2-4 business days - $12.00

Delivery Status

To check the delivery status of your order, please check the order history in your Reebok account or check Shipping Confirmation in your email.

Return Policy

  • Return your order within 30 days of receiving it using a free shipping label and get a full refund.
  • Merchandise must be new or unused with box and tags attached.
  • Face Covers, personalized products, and any products marked as final sale on the product page are not eligible for returns or exchanges.
  • All merchandise purchased through a discount promotion (for example, Buy One Get One Half Off) will be exchanged or returned at the value purchased. Price adjustments will be made for products not being returned within the promotion.

Return Process

  • P.O. Box and Military APO/FPO items will be shipped via USPS within 3-8 full business days. Business days are Monday - Friday, excluding federal holidays within the United States.

Gift Cards

  • We now feature Self Service Returns; click here for more information.
  • Remember to use a free shipping return label within 30 days for a full refund.

Order Processing

Once you place an order, we begin processing it immediately so that your gear arrives fast. You can’t change or cancel an order that’s already been placed, but you can return item(s) you don’t want.

  • We ship orders Monday - Friday. If you select next day shipping and submit the order after 12pm (EST), Monday - Friday, it won’t be processed until the next business day
  • If you place an order after 12pm (EST), Friday - Sunday and select next day shipping or two day shipping, it will ship Monday morning.
  • We'll send you a confirmation email once your order has been placed and processed. The confirmation will contain your order number, your shipping address, and the tracking number. Please remember to check your spam folder.
  • You will receive separate emails for product and Gift Card orders.

Payment Security

We use industry-leading technology to keep your credit card secure. Please review Reebok's Privacy Policyfor more details.

Norton Shopping Guarantee

We provide Norton Shopping Guarantee, which means that you will receive free:

  • ID Theft Protection
  • Purchase Guarantee
  • Lowest Price Guarantee

Here's how to claim your discount:

  • Pick a product (one that's applicable for a promotion discount) from our online store.
  • Go to your shopping cart by clicking the ‘shopping cart’ icon at the top of the screen.
  • Click the ‘Promo Code’ field in the Shopping Cart page.
  • A promotion code field will appear. Type your promotion code into the field and hit ‘Apply'.

Keep in mind the promotion code:

  • Is only valid for a limited time.
  • Might contain product exclusions and exceptions.
  • Cannot be applied after you've placed an order.
  • Cannot be combined with other promotions, offers or discounts. If more than one promotion or discount offer applies to your order, we'll use the one with the largest discount.

It’s easy to make mistakes if you enter the code manually. Some common mistakes are:

  • Check spacing, character errors and/or spelling mistakes.
  • The promotion code field is case-sensitive. Check that ‘Caps Lock’ button is not on and use upper case where necessary.
  • Check to make sure you’re not mixing up the numbers 0/1 and the letters O/I.
  • CPlease read the specific Terms and Conditions in the source of the promotion to make sure that your promotion applies to your order. If you are sure the promotion is valid for your order but it still doesn’t work, then please contact us.

Customer Care Hours

Call us: 1-866-870-1743 (free for landlines)

Mon – Fri: 8:00 am to 8:00 pm EST

Sat – Sun: 11:00 am to 7:00 pm EST

Chat with us: Please use the chat button on the lower right hand corner.

Sun – Sat: 8:00 am to 11:00 pm ET
